text: Đặng Anh Tuấn (born 1 August 1994) is a Vietnamese footballer who plays as a midfielder for V-League (Vietnam) club SHB Đà Nẵng. == References == Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Vietnamese footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:V.League 1 players Category:SHB Da Nang F.C. players
